# --- Power BI Project (PBIP) local state ---
**/.pbi/localSettings.json
**/.pbi/cache.abf
**/*.abf

# --- OS / editor noise ---
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~

# --- Datasets ---
# By default the pasted source data IS kept in the repo (the user asked for each report's
# dataset to be retained for future reference). If a report's raw data is large or sensitive,
# uncomment the matching line to exclude it (the dataset/samples/ folder should stay committed
# so the model can still be profiled / built in CI):
# reports/*/dataset/raw/*.csv
# reports/*/dataset/raw/*.parquet
# reports/*/dataset/raw/*.xlsx

# --- Python tooling (validate_pbip.py etc.) ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.env

# --- Editors / IDE ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace

# Note: raw dummy data under reports/*/dataset/raw/ is committed on purpose (reproducible demo).
# For FUTURE large/binary datasets, prefer Git LFS from the first commit, or commit only a
# trimmed copy under dataset/samples/ and uncomment the raw excludes above.
